data.description:
Odaily Planet Daily News Aptos published an article on the X platform stating that the lending protocol PACT has officially bridged to Aptos, bringing $1 billion worth of on-chain assets to Aptos. The PACT protocol aims to leverage Aptos' ultra-low-cost infrastructure to connect billions of underserved borrowers directly to global capital markets.
The next steps for the PACT protocol on Aptos are:
• Migration of PACT tokens to Aptos;
• Providing a 1:1 token bridge for holders;
• Future governance transitions and updates;
• Establishing a strategic and technical partnership with Aptos to speed things up.
